This paper deals with image classification using neural networks, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses data augmentation and optimization strategies for improving classification performance, which are topics commonly studied in machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE). Finally, the paper presents experimental results on ImageNet, which is a popular dataset in multimedia (cs.MM).
